    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a fantastic universe, form a group of up to 5 dwarves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a class then set off on an adventure in mines and galleries. Your goal is to extract materials there. However one of you finds yourself infected, and becomes a creature whose goal is to prevent his former colleagues from leaving again... Survive by working as a team but also by using your environment, your equipment and your skills to escape and trick your worst nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the monster's point of view you must evolve, move on the walls and ceilings. Use your skills to set traps, locate them, hide or hit your targets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be the hunter or the prey?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interactive Lobby </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character Customization </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free Cosmetics </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements to Unlock</p></li></ul>",
